QuestData.Title: With A Little Help From My Friends
QuestData.Description:
It has been so long since we have been able to trust anyone not in our little pack of survivors.
I forgot how good it feels.
Thank you for reminding me.
Atolia should have the rest of your gift together by now. We should go check in with her!
QuestData.LogDescription: Visit Atolia Seapearl, in Newhome, for your gift.
